verbose_text: Treatment of primary osteoblasts or osteoblastic cell lines (Saos-2 or MC3T3-E1) with recombinant CTGF stimulates proliferation, matrix production, mineralization, and up-regulates the expression of markers of osteoblast differentiation including type I collagen, osteopontin, osteocalcin and alkaline phosphatase [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
